HMeasure                Computes the H-measure, AUC, and several other
                        scalar classification performance metrics.
hmeasure-package        The H-measure and other classification
                        performance metrics
misclassCounts          Computes misclassification counts and related
                        statistics by contrasting predicted with true
                        class labels.
plotROC                 Plotting function illustrating the H-measure of
                        classification performance.
relabel                 Converts class labels to the default choice of
                        numeric 0s and 1s
summary.hmeasure        Report performance measures using an object of
                        class "hmeasure"
